dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.cbe.loc.local.LocalLocation
dataStructure.description:
A defined place defined by a local coordinate system.It is an abstract modeling concept that provides a linking point to other parts of the SID model.It holds attributes common to all Local Location subclasses.

This entity is abstract

This entity is optional
